nties. The same approach can be applied to the decay Bs→K $\nu$ to provide an alternative determination of |Vub| once the process has been measured experimentally. Finally, in anticipation of future experimental measurements, we make predictions for B→$\pi$ $\nu$ and Bs→K $\nu$ differential branching fractions and forward-backward asymmetries in the Standard Model.},
